<div1 type="section">
            <p>You are entirely welcome to use the <choice><abbr>eng:</abbr><expan>engraving</expan></choice> as you desire. I am about as usual&#8212;not any worse. Feel or fancy I feel, 
                relief already as summer wanes&#8212;one of my doctors</p></div1><div1 type="section"><p>thinks much of my head trouble the past three mos. is from the sun. 
                    I am almost always easier as day departs</p></div1><pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01803.001.jpg" type="verso"/>
                
       
